rows.label: qev070303_MSG0001
rows.name:
You can do whatever you want—you're not getting
anything out of me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0002
rows.name:
Gadd, was it? If you hate me that much,
man up and kill me, you sorry little #a+3«»%![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Professor B that you've come to help him.

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0003
rows.name:
Good heavens—[ST:playername ]!
Did Veven send you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0004
rows.name:
Wup, wup, whew! I thought this might finally be the
mission I didn't make it back from.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0005
rows.name:
Frankly, I pity you. You haven't a talented bone in your
body, so instead you kidnap geniuses and sell them off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0006
rows.name:
Does the patheticness of that haunt you when you lie in
bed at night? No matter how many people you sell,
you'll still be a whiny little #a+3«»%.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0007
rows.name:
Hold on a second. You're not Gadd.
I know that voice from—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0008
rows.name:
Is that you, [ST:playername ]?
Yes, this is absolutely your frequency![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0009
rows.name:
Well, if you're done playing stupid pranks,
hurry up and get me out of here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0010
rows.name:
I can fill you in on the situation once we're out of here.
But first you've got to get the gray keycard that disables
this barrier![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0011
rows.name: A Marnuck around here should be carrying it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0012
rows.name: This is a very important task for you, kid.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0013
rows.name:
Now that I'm a CEO, I'm a very busy man—
and I can't waste any more of my time here.
I've got new products to flog to the masses![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0014
rows.name:
Wup, wup?! Did you forget?
A Marnuck has the gray keycard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070303_MSG0015
rows.name: Take him down, secure it, and get me out of here, kid![ST:wait ]
